Properties.Caption: Просмотр отчетов об исполнении-внебюджетные расходы
Properties.Tag: Select [K_TD].[CTD] As [Тип документа], Max([K_TD].[NTD]) As [Наименование типа документа], [Apps_Groups].[GroupName] As [Группа], [DOC].[CDOC] As [Документ], [K_TD_SUB].[CTD_SUB] As [Подтип], Max([K_TD_SUB].[NTD_SUB]) As [Наименование подтипа], [K_UL_1].[ADM] As [АДМ], [K_PS].[CPS] As [Код ОСГУ], Max([K_PS].[NPS]) As [Наименование ОСГУ], Sum([REP].[SUMM02]) As [Графа 02], Sum([REP].[SUMM03]) As [Графа 03], Sum([REP].[SUMM05]) As [Графа 05], Sum([REP].[SUMM06]) As [Графа 06] From ((((((((((([REP] With (NoLock) Inner Join [DOC] With (NoLock) On ([REP].[DOCID]=[DOC].[DOCID])) Inner Join [Apps_Groups] With (NoLock) On ([DOC].[Apps_GroupsID]=[Apps_Groups].[Apps_GroupsID])) Inner Join [K_UL_K_UL] With (NoLock) On ([DOC].[K_UL_K_ULID]=[K_UL_K_UL].[K_UL_K_ULID])) Inner Join [K_UL] With (NoLock) On ([K_UL_K_UL].[K_ULID]=[K_UL].[K_ULID])) Inner Join [K_UL] As [K_UL_PARENT] With (NoLock) On ([K_UL_K_UL].[K_ULID_PARENT]=[K_UL_PARENT].[K_ULID])) Inner Join [Apps_Groups_K_UL_K_UL] With (NoLock) On ([K_UL_K_UL].[K_UL_K_ULID]=[Apps_Groups_K_UL_K_UL].[K_UL_K_ULID])) Inner Join [K_UL] As [K_UL_1] With (NoLock) On ([REP].[ID1]=[K_UL_1].[K_ULID])) Inner Join [K_PS] With (NoLock) On ([REP].[ID2]=[K_PS].[K_PSID])) Inner Join [K_PERIOD] With (NoLock) On ([REP].[K_PERIODID]=[K_PERIOD].[K_PERIODID])) Inner Join [K_TD_SUB] With (NoLock) On ([REP].[K_TD_SUBID]=[K_TD_SUB].[K_TD_SUBID])) Inner Join [K_TD] With (NoLock) On ([K_TD_SUB].[K_TDID]=[K_TD].[K_TDID])) Where [Apps_Groups_K_UL_K_UL].[Apps_GroupsID]=GetApps_GroupsID() And [K_TD_SUB].[CTD_SUB] In ('165') And [REP].[SUMM_TYPE]=0 And |0 Group by [K_TD].[CTD], [Apps_Groups].[GroupName], [DOC].[CDOC], [K_TD_SUB].[CTD_SUB], [K_UL_1].[ADM], [K_PS].[CPS] Order by |1
Properties.Name: Просмотр отчетов об исполнении-внебюджетные расходы
